title: Greenfield Finder - Updated!
description:
The Greenfield Finder Application has been updated with the following:
•	Ability to enter specific address as location of interest
•	A blue ‘pin’ is shown in the maps indicating the address entered
•	15, 20, 30 and 45-minute drive time boundaries added to Maps – Drive Time boundaries, zip codes and associated deliveries shown at all distances
•	12-month Delivery Sales data is aggregated at the various drive time boundaries
•	Increased width of maps for better visibility

All of these are found within the “Location Reports” section of the application.
